# 🎨 Figma Design to Website (HTML, CSS, JS)

This project is a front-end implementation of a Figma design I created.  
I converted the design **exactly as it was** into a responsive website using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.

---

## 🚀 Project Overview

- 🎨 **Figma to Code** — The template was built pixel-perfect based on my original Figma design.
- 💻 **HTML** — Used for the structure and layout of all pages.
- 🎨 **CSS** — Heavily focused on styling, animations, and responsiveness.
- ⚙️ **JavaScript (Basic)** — Used for small interactions like toggles, buttons, and minor animations.

